  "text": "Particularly interesting are the R 4 -couplings [CITATION_1] because they are BPS protected and can only receive contributions from string tree-level, one-loop and non-perturbative effects. Let us first discuss in general what one might learn about the light-like limit from these couplings and then consider the explicit results of [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
